@Tom, you&#39;re problem actually may be this:

var rootNodes = currentPage.AncestorsOrSelf.Last().Children;

try changing to:

var rootNodes = currentPage.AncestorsOrSelf.Last().Children.ToArray()

you are trying to iterate through the same child block numerous times, this is very inneficieint and may not actually work.

